## Limitations

This report is based on information available up to October 2023, and the rapidly evolving nature of technology and cyber threats may lead to new risks and safeguards not covered in this document. Additionally, some sources may not provide the most recent data or comprehensive coverage of all potential risks and safeguards associated with wireless communication.